InvalidEntityException - Exception in il.ac.ariel.liortamir.javalab.exception
This exception is thrown in case the Entity in a request
cannot be found or an invalid Charge type is passed to ChargeFactory.

InvalidStateException - Exception in il.ac.ariel.liortamir.javalab.exception
This exception is thrown in case a request contains event which does not match
the associated Charge state.
It is the default exception implemented in AbstractStateHandler
logical methods.
